snippet.title: Sturmwind Normal Mode Normal Difficulty 1CC Sega Dreamcast
snippet.description:
Recently I went back to the excellent Sturmwind on the Sega Dreamcast and I finally managed to beat the normal mode on normal difficulty with one credit and considering this game offers a pretty solid challenge I wasn't sure if I could pull it off but I finally did! If you want to see my other play through's of Sturmwind including beating the arcade mode on hard the links are below! 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UwT7kf-kAuE&list=PLFjgQp_M8uDKvTBE5C-6iK8hjtj0t4afO&index=9

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8rklfMklb88&list=PLFjgQp_M8uDKvTBE5C-6iK8hjtj0t4afO&index=10
